            <li class="text-neutral-700 font-semibold marker:text-fuchsia-950">
              Plot for outright sale at Rs 30k per sqm
            </li>
            <li class="text-neutral-700 font-semibold marker:text-fuchsia-950">
              For Commercial space for rent available furniture manufacture and
              showroom, hardware building material or tile showroom at rent 1.5
              L monthly
            </li>
